<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN203-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. cēramāṉ pāḻalūreṟinta neytalaṅkāṉaliḷañcēṭceṉṉiyai ūṉpotipacuṅkuṭaiyār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN203">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaḻintatu poḻinteṉa vāṉkaṇ māṟiṉun</l>
<l>tollatu viḷainteṉa nilamvaḷaṅ karappiṉu</l>
<l>mellā vuyirkku millāl vāḻkkai</l>
<l>yiṉṉun tammeṉa vemmaṉō rirappiṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉuṅ koṇṭireṉa nummaṉōr maṟutta</l>
<l>liṉṉā tamma viyaṟē raṇṇa</l>
<l>lillatu nirappa lāṟṟā tōriṉu</l>
<l>muḷḷi varunar nacaiyiḻap pōrē</l>
<l>yaṉaiyaiyu mallai nīyē yoṉṉā</l>
<l>rāreyi lavarkaṭ ṭākavu numateṉap</l>
<l>pāṇkaṭa ṉiṟukkum vaḷḷiyōy</l>
<l>pūṇkaṭa ṉentainī yiravalar puravē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">If, because in the past [rain] flew, the clouds changed area, </l>
<l corresp="2">if because it ripened of old, the soil would hide [its] fertility, </l>
<l corresp="3">there would be no living for all the beings. </l>
<l corresp="4">If the likes of us beg “give [us something] yet again”, </l>
<l corresp="5">the likes of you refusing “you took before” </l>
<l corresp="6">is unpleasant, ah, majesty with an advancing chariot. </l>
<l corresp="7">More than those who are not able to fill what is not there </l>
<l corresp="8">there are those who lose the love for those who come, remembering, </l>
<l corresp="9a-c">and you are not like that. </l>
<l corresp="11">You capable of performing [your] duty to bards, </l>
<l corresp="9d-10">saying “the enemy fortress difficult [to break], being their place is [now] your’s.” </l>
<l>You, father of ornamental virtue, are the protection for supplicants.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
